00:00:38.960 --> 00:00:41.330
That's not quite right, boy.

00:00:41.330 --> 00:00:43.460
Huh? It's not?

00:00:43.790 --> 00:00:49.210
It's true I think of sucking blood like eating,
but it's also a way to make offspring.

00:00:49.710 --> 00:00:50.920
Under certain conditions,

00:00:50.920 --> 00:00:53.830
drinking a person's blood can turn them into a vampire,

00:00:53.830 --> 00:00:56.210
and that's how we vampires produce more offspring.

00:00:57.750 --> 00:00:58.960
Which means...

00:01:00.630 --> 00:01:05.080
Sucking blood is like eating and
copulating at the same time!

00:01:08.210 --> 00:01:10.830
Why do you always say copulating?

00:01:11.210 --> 00:01:13.000
Huh? You don't know?

00:01:13.000 --> 00:01:16.170
Copulating means to unite the stamen and the pistil...

00:01:16.170 --> 00:01:18.670
I know that!
That's not what I mean!

00:01:19.830 --> 00:01:23.500
Come on, have you forgotten your objective?

00:01:24.040 --> 00:01:25.830
Why are you here, anyway?

00:01:27.920 --> 00:01:31.290
Well, not that I care either way.

00:01:31.920 --> 00:01:33.500
Of course I remember.

00:01:33.500 --> 00:01:35.210
It's what I want to be someday.

00:01:36.040 --> 00:01:37.920
I want to be a vampire.

00:01:38.420 --> 00:01:39.710
That's why I'm here.

00:01:39.710 --> 00:01:41.460
Got it, got it!

00:01:41.460 --> 00:01:41.880
That's why...

00:01:41.880 --> 00:01:43.170
I said I got it!
That's why...<b></b>

00:01:43.170 --> 00:01:46.080
...I need to fall in love with you, Nazuna Nanakusa!

00:01:46.080 --> 00:01:47.960
I got it, jeez!

00:01:50.880 --> 00:01:54.170
So what's your request, then?

00:01:55.330 --> 00:01:59.790
When I said I wanted to be a vampire,
you were about to say something.

00:02:00.250 --> 00:02:01.460
Your blood...

00:02:01.460 --> 00:02:03.210
I just want another taste.

00:02:03.960 --> 00:02:05.460
Okay, sure.

00:02:05.460 --> 00:02:06.670
Want some now?

00:02:07.000 --> 00:02:08.210
H-hey!

00:02:08.210 --> 00:02:09.750
Why would you show me that?!

00:02:09.750 --> 00:02:11.250
You perv! You slutty perv!

00:02:12.040 --> 00:02:13.710
Man, you took me by surprise...

00:02:13.710 --> 00:02:15.290
Cover that up, quick.

00:02:16.000 --> 00:02:18.250
You're such a kinky kid, you know that?

00:02:18.460 --> 00:02:20.580
What the heck are you talking about?

00:02:20.580 --> 00:02:22.040
