00:02:28.880 --> 00:02:31.290
Besides, you gotta think about timing.

00:02:32.380 --> 00:02:33.580
Timing?

00:02:36.540 --> 00:02:41.670
<i>When a person falls in love with a vampire
and has that vampire drink their blood,</i>

00:02:41.670 --> 00:02:43.670
<i>only then will they turn into a vampire.</i>

00:02:44.460 --> 00:02:47.460
<i>In other words, if the person thinks
nothing of the vampire,</i>

00:02:47.460 --> 00:02:50.250
<i>they'll stay human no matter how much blood they give.</i>

00:02:50.790 --> 00:02:54.380
<i>That's why I have to fall in love with her.</i>

00:02:55.460 --> 00:02:58.460
<i>This is the story of my quest to fall in love...</i>

00:02:59.000 --> 00:03:00.210
<i>with a vampire.</i>

00:03:05.380 --> 00:03:07.380
Hey, did you know?

00:03:09.330 --> 00:03:12.670
Your blood tastes super good.

