00:05:31.380 --> 00:05:32.880
<i>I'll go back near my place...</i>

00:05:33.380 --> 00:05:34.960
<i>and look for Nanakusa-san.</i>

00:05:43.420 --> 00:05:48.670
<i>But even if she sucks my blood now,
it's not like I'll get to be a vampire.</i>

00:05:49.750 --> 00:05:53.000
