so I'm all tired out!

00:09:02.250 --> 00:09:03.960
Hey, what are you waiting for?

00:09:07.040 --> 00:09:08.580
Come join me already.

00:09:19.040 --> 00:09:20.750
<i>I really dunno.</i>

00:09:21.330 --> 00:09:23.500
<i>I mean, I'm not in love yet or anything...</i>

00:09:24.380 --> 00:09:28.420
<i>Besides, anyone would be flustered in this situation.</i>

00:09:29.540 --> 00:09:34.080
<i>Isn't it normal that I don't want her
doing this with other people?</i>

00:09:35.580 --> 00:09:36.790
Hey, you...

00:09:37.210 --> 00:09:39.420
