with blood as tasty as yours.

00:10:42.040 --> 00:10:43.040
Here...

00:11:03.500 --> 00:11:05.670
<i>I realized I felt relieved.</i>

00:11:06.880 --> 00:11:11.170
<i>Not because my blood is tasty,
but because we both felt the same way.</i>

00:11:14.210 --> 00:11:16.500
