just because I don't have any friends!

00:13:20.580 --> 00:13:22.380
I see; sorry.

00:13:24.790 --> 00:13:26.210
Here's what happened.

00:13:26.960 --> 00:13:29.210
I think it was when I was nine.

00:13:30.250 --> 00:13:32.830
"These are totally gonna be fun, and cool!"

00:13:33.290 --> 00:13:35.580
