00:19:46.170 --> 00:19:47.790
Aww, man!

00:19:47.790 --> 00:19:49.460
It's really so tasty!

00:19:50.460 --> 00:19:51.710
<i>Somehow...</i>

00:19:51.710 --> 00:19:53.080
